data.description: Location, location, location!!! Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedrooms, 2 baths home with an elegant elevation!  It is situated near the end of the cul-de-sac.  It features an open floor plan with a very welcoming and comfortable living space, family room or office, an extensive (primary) bedroom, spacious closet, bathtub, and stand-up shower.  It features an outstanding and enclosed back patio for outdoor gathering and entertainment.   Around the community, there are walking trails, a soccer field, schools nearby, and a basketball court.  Don't miss out on this great opportunity. Schedule now.
